Discovery Predict Transformation: Get Einstein Discovery Predictions

In CRM Analytics, use the Discovery Predict transformation to populate your datasets with predictive and prescriptive intelligence. When you run a Data Prep recipe with a Discovery Predict node, Einstein calculates and saves predicted outcomes on a row-by-row basis.

To create a recipe: Edit Analytics Dataflows OR Edit Dataset Recipes
To view predictions, improvements, and related details: View Einstein Discovery Recommendations

Edit a Data Prep recipe.
Where you want to insert the node, click Add Node (+) and choose Discovery Predict.
Select a deployed prediction, then click Next.
Map all fields from the prediction to the recipe.

If you want to include prediction and improvement text in the dataset, click the Options subtab.
Top predictors Enable Top predictors and specify the number of entries you want to save to the dataset.
Top improvements Enable Top improvements and specify the number of entries you want to save to the dataset.

Click Apply.

Einstein adds the Discovery Predict node to your recipe.

Save the recipe.

Run the recipe to get predictions.
title: Discovery Predict Transformation in CRM Analytics
